title: Arktoons Six Million
author: VD
content_html:
Arkhaven Comics is pleased to announce that Arktoons has recorded more than 6 million pageviews since its launch less than one year ago. Thanks very much to the subscribers, the dev team, the production team, and the creators who have made it all possible!
